{
  "text": "EpCAM has also been found in migrating embryonic and neonatal germ cells, whereas, terminally differentiated germ cells in adult mice cease to express EpCAM [CITATION_1] . Also rodent embryonic stem cells (ES cells) produce EpCAM (personal observation by M. Trzpis and (13, [CITATION_2] ",
